headline: Obviousness For Designs Is Now The Same As Inventions/Utility Patents
summary: In LKQ Corp. et al. v. GM Global Technology Operations LLC,1 the Federal Circuit held, on rehearing en banc, that obviousness of a patented design is determined based on the four-part obviousness test...
